name: QuasarII
description:
QuasarII or Quasar2 Dynamo Package contains simple(usage), reliable(performance) and useful(productive) Nodes for your daily dynamo operation on Revit. View Extension included for utility tools to organize nodes and graphs. 
The latest QuasarII package built on Dynamo 2.5.0 & Revit 2021. Please go to the website link for Nodes Information & Usage.

Version Update : include sample files.
